item.title: CVE-2021-26610|2024-08-03T20:26:25.468Z -- nhn%20commerce -- godomall5%20std%2C%20godomall5%20pro
item.description: The move_uploaded_file function in godomall5 does not perform an integrity check of extension or authority when user upload file. This vulnerability allows an attacker to execute an remote arbitrary code.
